WEBVTT

00:01.069 --> 00:03.012
In the criminal justice system

00:03.085 --> 00:04.711
sexually-based offenses

00:04.782 --> 00:06.440
are considered especially heinous.

00:06.509 --> 00:08.779
In New York City,
the dedicated detectives...

00:08.845 --> 00:10.537
who investigate these vicious felonies

00:10.606 --> 00:12.199
are members of an elite squad

00:12.270 --> 00:13.896
known as the Special Victims Unit.

00:13.966 --> 00:15.460
These are their stories.

00:19.598 --> 00:22.446
Come on, Annie.
Just one little drink.

00:22.511 --> 00:24.877
I can't.
I smell like French fries.

00:24.943 --> 00:26.470
I love French fries.

00:26.543 --> 00:29.326
I appreciate the offer, Butch,
but my feet are killing me.

00:29.392 --> 00:32.458
I just want to take a hot bath
and curl up with my People.

00:32.528 --> 00:35.048
Maybe next time. All
right, I'll hold you to it.

00:35.120 --> 00:37.127
MaÃ±ana.

00:38.704 --> 00:41.606
I love French fries.
How stupid.

00:45.329 --> 00:46.442
Annie?

00:50.801 --> 00:53.005
Back off!
Okay.

00:57.329 --> 00:59.664
Get off me!
Let him go!

01:03.089 --> 01:05.129
Hey, come back here!

01:06.355 --> 01:08.078
Stop!
Annie!

01:14.196 --> 01:17.425
Abductee's name is Annie Tassler.
A waitress at the diner over there.

01:17.490 --> 01:19.346
Why'd you bring us
in on a snatch job?

01:19.411 --> 01:20.906
Found this on the scene.

01:20.979 --> 01:23.085
Chloroform? Dropped it in the struggle.

01:23.156 --> 01:25.939
Took off in a green
four-by-four. Witnesses?

01:26.004 --> 01:28.208
Butch McGee,
a hash slinger at the diner...

01:28.277 --> 01:31.026
and a Good Samaritan
by the name of Marty Potter.

01:31.092 --> 01:33.777
They took their lumps
trying to stop him. Thanks.

01:33.845 --> 01:35.252
There's something
I'm missing?

01:35.317 --> 01:39.028
Last summer, a guy abducted
four women using the same M.O.

01:39.094 --> 01:40.338
Raped and tortured them.

01:40.405 --> 01:42.893
Left their bodies stacked in
a warehouse in Alphabet City.

01:42.965 --> 01:44.526
The Bowery Stalker?
One and the same.

01:44.598 --> 01:46.508
I haven't heard about that guy
in a long time.

01:46.582 --> 01:47.924
Not long enough.

01:47.990 --> 01:49.846
Butch, Marty?
Yeah. I'm Butch.

01:49.910 --> 01:51.698
What do you got for us?

01:51.862 --> 01:53.269
He pulled her
right off the street.

01:53.335 --> 01:54.611
Did you get
a good look at him?

01:54.678 --> 01:56.686
He's a big guy with a beard
and a baseball cap.

01:56.758 --> 01:57.773
You ever seen him before?

01:57.847 --> 01:59.669
He might've been
in the diner a few times...

01:59.734 --> 02:01.710
but I never really
got a good look at his face.

02:01.784 --> 02:02.765
How do you
fit into all this?

02:02.840 --> 02:04.149
Saw the commotion,
tried to help.

02:04.216 --> 02:05.198
You have something to add?

02:05.272 --> 02:08.621
Yeah. He had a tattoo. A cat of
some sort on his right forearm.

02:08.695 --> 02:11.062
I saw it coming at me when
he shoved the gun in my face.

02:11.128 --> 02:13.779
If I put you with a sketch
artist, can you give us a picture?

02:13.848 --> 02:15.441
I can try.
Sure.

02:15.641 --> 02:18.008
We gotta get them in the bus.
Go.

02:18.328 --> 02:20.662
How long you think the
Stalker will keep her alive?

02:20.760 --> 02:22.865
Until he's finished with her.

